  "description": "<i>Happy Salvage</i> is a treasure hunting romantic adventure game that uses 3rd-person perspective for exploring places and diving underwater to collect treasure, with visual novel style 1st-person perspective during dialogues featuring anime characters over static backgrounds. On your adventure you will meet many girls who will be able to go and dive with you, and while the game starts on a single island, over time you'll be able to sail to other islands and explore other places. The game comes on two discs, where second disc contains various bonus content, such as character profiles, game artwork and other game trailers and previews.",
